    "seo_collection_desc_soft_muse": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<div style=\"background:#fff;\"><div class=\"container\"><div class=\"seo-collection-description\" style=\"padding:32px 0 24px;\">\n  <p style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:1.8;color:#444;max-width:800px;\">\n    Soft Muse is a love letter to femininity — gentle, joyful, and unapologetically pretty. This collection brings together ZUVE's most delicate designs: pastel pinks and nudes, watercolour florals, abstract blooms, and soft-toned nail art that works beautifully from morning coffee to evening events.\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"font-size:15px;line-height:1.8;color:#555;max-width:800px;margin-top:12px;\">\n    Every Soft Muse set is built on our premium soft gel base — flexible, lightweight, and designed to look like a professional nail extension. Apply in 10 minutes. Reuse them for weeks. Perfect for daily wear, bridal sets, mehndi, and gifting. 30 nails per set &middot; 15 sizes &middot; Free shipping above &#8377;1,500 &middot; COD available.\n  </p>\n</div></div></div>"
      }
    }
